title: ICYMI - Tammy Duckworth on Sustaining Businesses and Communities in Illinois During the Pandemic
itunes:title: ICYMI - Tammy Duckworth on Sustaining Businesses and Communities in Illinois During the Pandemic
description:
Illinois Sen. Tammy Duckworth discusses her efforts to aid small businesses during the COVID-19 crisis and the health issues disproportionately affecting communities of color.
